### Создать token
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/token
Content-Type: application/json

### Получить jobs
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/job
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJpc3MiOiJzb25hbnoiLCJpYXQiOjE3ODI3NTg3MDMsImV4cCI6MTc4Mjc2MjMwMywic3ViIjoiMDE5ZjE0YjMtMDI4Yy03NmQzLWJkZmQtMWM2NWMxZjc5MzNlIn0.eUu6sr86I2sU2n7ABz5-mq9tISipUXon9l1PWp5FhbM

